to buy me dessert.

39
00:03:54,088 --> 00:03:58,555
Because I'm getting old.

40
00:03:58,655 --> 00:03:59,988
Huh?

41
00:04:00,088 --> 00:04:02,255
It's about time I
handpicked someone

