Ryoga's fiance.

107
00:07:43,488 --> 00:07:44,755
RYOGA (VOICEOVER): My fiance?

108
00:07:44,855 --> 00:07:47,322
SOUN: I suppose
it's only natural.

109
00:07:47,422 --> 00:07:51,588
KASUMI: I'm so happy
for you, Akane.

110
00:07:51,688 --> 00:07:53,522
Don't I even have
a say in this?

111
00:07:59,055 --> 00:08:00,955
Akane.

112
00:08:01,055 --> 00:08:03,255
[grunting]

113
00:08:12,322 --> 00:08:13,688
RANMA (VOICEOVER):
Stupid old man.

114
00:08:13,788 --> 00:08:16,155
Dragging Ryoga into this.

115
