what you're thinking.

121
00:08:56,122 --> 00:08:58,022
But when you come to
your senses, Pops,

122
00:08:58,122 --> 00:09:00,288
would you please let me know?

123
00:09:00,388 --> 00:09:02,855
Maybe it's you who should
come to his senses, boy.

124
