When you realize
what you've done,

125
00:09:09,122 --> 00:09:11,222
perhaps then you'll
admit your mistake

126
00:09:11,322 --> 00:09:13,355
and ask for forgiveness.

127
00:09:13,455 --> 00:09:15,355
That's all I have to say.

128
00:09:31,055 --> 00:09:33,922
