let all of this happen to me.

129
00:09:37,588 --> 00:09:39,555
Oh, we're out of milk.

130
00:09:39,655 --> 00:09:40,855
RANMA: You can't sleep, either?

131
00:09:40,955 --> 00:09:43,222
Huh?

132
00:09:43,322 --> 00:09:44,455
Ranma!

133
00:09:44,555 --> 00:09:45,688
You scared me.

134
00:09:45,788 --> 00:09:48,622
RANMA: You want me to go
out and get you some milk?

135
00:09:48,722 --> 00:09:49,755
Oh, that's OK.

136
00:09:49,855 --> 00:09:50,955
It's pretty late.

137
00:09:51,055 --> 00:09:53,255
Hey, I think the corner
store is still open.

138
00:09:56,522 --> 00:09:57,955
It's OK, really.

139
00:10:00,588 --> 00:10:01,722
CLERK: Thank you for shopping.

140
00:10:01,822 --> 00:10:04,788
