146
00:10:30,655 --> 00:10:31,922
Thank you, master.

147
00:10:32,022 --> 00:10:35,222
Oh yes, I like that
when you call me master.

148
00:10:35,322 --> 00:10:38,888
Master, I personally
guarantee I can beat Ranma.

149
00:10:38,988 --> 00:10:42,722
Ryoga, I must confess it pains
me a great deal that I have

150
00:10:42,822 --> 00:10:44,955
disgraced my own flesh
and blood by telling you

151
00:10:45,055 --> 00:10:47,322
all of his weak points,
so that you can embarrass

152
00:10:47,422 --> 00:10:49,455
that boy of mine in public.

153
00:10:49,555 --> 00:10:53,222
But I'm must for the
good of my school.

154
00:10:53,322 --> 00:10:54,922
Then I cannot fail you.

155
00:10:59,122 --> 00:11:00,222
Ryoga, look.

156
00:11:00,322 --> 00:11:03,155
That star represents
my entire empire.

157
00:11:03,255 --> 00:11:05,655
Your mission is
to reach up for it

158
00:11:05,755 --> 00:11:09,222
and become the new shining
star of the Saotome School.

159
00:11:11,722 --> 00:11:12,163
RYOGA: OK.

160
00:11:31,629 --> 00:11:33,963
So has your dad moved
back into the house?

161
00:11:34,063 --> 00:11:35,229
Who cares?

162
00:11:35,329 --> 00:11:39,696
