lousy tent, I say let him.

163
00:11:39,796 --> 00:11:42,296
Ranma, do you think
there's a chance that Ryoga

164
00:11:42,396 --> 00:11:44,796
is going to take over
your father's school?

165
00:11:44,896 --> 00:11:47,629
[grunting]

166
00:11:49,629 --> 00:11:52,163
Stay on your toes, boy.

167
00:11:52,263 --> 00:11:55,563
[grunting]

168
00:12:00,929 --> 00:12:02,763
Listen carefully, Ryoga.

169
00:12:02,863 --> 00:12:04,729
In order to defeat
Ranma, you must

170
00:12:04,829 --> 00:12:06,129
learn his special techniques.

171
00:12:10,896 --> 00:12:12,296
That's it, Ryoga.

172
00:12:12,396 --> 00:12:13,296
Keep going.

173
00:12:13,396 --> 00:12:17,529
Harder, harder, feel the burn.

174
00:12:17,629 --> 00:12:18,496
That's it.

175
00:12:28,929 --> 00:12:31,129
They seem pretty serious.

176
00:12:31,229 --> 00:12:32,096
Hm.

177
00:12:32,196 --> 00:12:33,563
Huh Hey, wait.

