Oh, and from the
rumors going around,

191
00:13:12,496 --> 00:13:14,329
Ranma, is it true
that Ryoga is going

192
00:13:14,429 --> 00:13:16,429
to take over your dad's school?

193
00:13:16,529 --> 00:13:17,663
