199
00:13:25,929 --> 00:13:28,463
Yeah, I suppose
she has a point.

200
00:13:28,563 --> 00:13:29,763
Hey, I got an idea.

201
00:13:29,863 --> 00:13:31,329
You could move in with me.

202
