okonomiyaki is on the house.

210
00:13:51,563 --> 00:13:54,129
Why, you jerk, Ranma!

211
00:13:58,563 --> 00:13:59,829
Calamari as usual?

212
00:13:59,929 --> 00:14:01,063
Sure.

213
00:14:01,163 --> 00:14:05,463
Or maybe something in to
help me keep up my strength.

214
00:14:05,563 --> 00:14:08,996
Ra-- Ranma, I mean, I know
that we've always been engaged

215
00:14:09,096 --> 00:14:12,429
and all, but it's so sudden.

216
00:14:12,529 --> 00:14:13,629
You know?

217
00:14:13,729 --> 00:14:17,363
Not that I, you know--
I'm so embarrassed.

218
00:14:17,463 --> 00:14:22,229
I bet Ryoga's going to
challenge me any day now.

219
00:14:22,329 --> 00:14:25,196
[grunting]

220
00:14:29,729 --> 00:14:30,178
Kick.

