Good one.

224
00:14:41,063 --> 00:14:44,396
[screaming]

225
00:14:51,963 --> 00:14:56,296
If you want to win, Ryoga, your
moves must be more precise.

226
00:14:56,396 --> 00:14:57,229
Right.

227
00:14:57,329 --> 00:14:59,896
But the hour fast
approaches when

228
00:14:59,996 --> 00:15:01,763
you must do battle with Ranma.

229
00:15:10,496 --> 00:15:12,629
