245
00:16:44,929 --> 00:16:48,663
Wow, I didn't think
Ryoga was that good.

246
00:16:48,763 --> 00:16:51,129
You're right.

247
00:16:51,229 --> 00:16:53,563
[gasping]

248
00:16:53,663 --> 00:16:56,529
