fighting toe-to-toe

250
00:16:58,263 --> 00:17:00,663
without so much as showing
any signs of tiring.

251
00:17:00,763 --> 00:17:03,563
And still the question remains
in this fight to the finish--

252
00:17:03,663 --> 00:17:05,563
who will be the
last one standing

253
00:17:05,663 --> 00:17:08,296
and win the honor of
being Akane's fiance?

254
00:17:21,663 --> 00:17:23,063
Come on, Ryoga!

255
00:17:23,163 --> 00:17:26,063
I'm cheering for you this time
for special personal reasons.

256
00:17:26,163 --> 00:17:27,696
